        <text class="p9-line p9-line-ok" wx:if="{{p9SuspectAllClear}}">无待落实事项</text>
        <block wx:else>
          <text class="p9-warn-item" wx:for="{{p9SuspectWarnings}}" wx:key="key">⚠️ {{item.warnMsg}}</text>
        </block>
      </view>

      <view class="p9-tip">
        <text>请核对以上信息，如有误请点「上一项」返回修改\n确认无误后点「下一项」生成测算结果</text>
      </view>
